WEBVTT

24:03.650 --> 24:05.192
But I have a small condition.

24:05.942 --> 24:06.817
What condition?

24:07.484 --> 24:07.984
Excuse me.

24:08.900 --> 24:10.400
-Please come here.
-Me?

24:10.692 --> 24:11.192
Yes.

24:11.525 --> 24:12.025
One minute.

24:12.359 --> 24:13.775
-Yeah you, come here.
-Yes?

24:16.359 --> 24:20.859
I want to marry someone with
lengthy and curly hair like him.

24:20.984 --> 24:22.109
That is my childhood dream.

24:22.234 --> 24:25.067
I cannot let go of that dream.
So can you grow hair like him?

24:25.359 --> 24:26.192
Like him?

24:26.234 --> 24:29.109
Yes, this is today's fashion.
Many movie hero's have this.
